COMMENT ON COLUMN negative_control_tests.negative_control_test_id IS 'Stable id for this control test.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN negative_control_tests.control_label IS 'Human label.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN negative_control_tests.causal_mechanism IS 'FK to the mechanism being controlled.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN negative_control_tests.test_kind IS 'OBSERVATION: kind of control (ancestry-permutation / batch-stratified / negative-control).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN negative_control_tests.permutation_effect_size IS 'OBSERVATION: (absolute) effect measured under the null/permuted control.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN negative_control_tests.null_threshold IS 'OBSERVATION: pre-registered null-band half-width the control must stay within.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN negative_control_tests.source_quote IS 'PANEL 2->1 provenance pointer (raw leaf, read by nothing downstream): the literal span of the patient''s CaseNarrative from which this negative control''s raw value was extracted. A human verifies the EXTRACTION was faithful here, separately from trusting the derived diagnosis — which is exactly what defeats ''a hallucination laundered through a deterministic function''.';

